# User Stories

1. As a beginner in my fitness journey, I want to get personalised workout routines for my body type so that I can work towards my ideal physiche.
2. As someone who needs recipe inspiration, I want to be able to search and filter recipes based on my dietary restrictions and protein content so that I can reach my nutritional goals. 
3. As a visual person, I need to be able to look at my body silouhette so that I can see which exercises will help target specific muscles
4. As a user tracking my progress, I want to log my workouts and meals so that I can monitor my improvements and stay accountable to my fitness goals.
